{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b913de3a34","title":"给西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议的复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"43b7faafc6","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"b913de3a34"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji6","name":"毛泽东文集第六卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji6":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aafa9d5d27","type":"title","text":"给西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议的复电","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"6c3d5f1ca2","type":"paragraph","text":"西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议全体代表同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"d7b010976b","type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你们给我的电报。过去一年多以来，西北区各族人民在抗美援朝的爱国斗争中，作了很大的努力，得到了很大的成绩。你们的这次代表会议，决定进一步团结各族人民，增加生产，厉行节约，开展爱国主义的宣传教育工作，以支持中国人民志愿军，这是很好的。帝国主义过去敢于欺负中国的原因之一，是中国各民族不团结，但是这个时代已经永远过去了，从中华人民共和国成立的那一天起，中国各民族就开始团结成为友爱合作的大家庭，足以战胜任何帝国主义的侵略，并且把我们的祖国建设成为繁荣强盛的国家。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"9411a6d2e4","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们的会议成功！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"e55faf672d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"ab32bb9f10","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十二日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"d636b12697","type":"paragraph","text":"根据一九五一年十二月十四日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"},{"id":"d463578fca","type":"paragraph","text":"《人民日报》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34"}],"page":{"id":"3d7111cde4","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"b913de3a34","start":225,"end":225}}}},"__N_SSG":true}